hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: Gloomy tales best drugstore foundation for discoloration In one of the early ones, I’m strapped in a seat on the back of my mom’s bike. On warm summer nights, when the air buzzed with humidity and cicadas, we would ride under streetlights to [Baskin-Robbins](http://baskinrobbins.com/). I didn’t even look at the 31 flavors — I was all about the chocolate clown cone, an upside-down chocolate cone with frosting hair and a cherry nose. The trick was eating the ice cream before the clown’s face melted into a sticky mess.
